<text top="704" left="122" width="146" height="14" font="1">The situation in Croatia</text>
<text top="740" left="153" width="675" height="14" font="1">Report of the Secretary-General pursuant to Security Council resolution 1043 (1996) (S/1996/472 and Add.1)</text>
